[sebaygo1]


Scheduled Guests

From the Infowars web site ::

 
In the lead-up to a rally at the Texas capitol this afternoon, Alex covers the latest breaking developments on a bill that would criminalize TSA groping of travelers. 

He also talks with Webster Tarpley from Libya and investigative journalist Wayne Madsen who recently returned from a fact-finding tour of the north African state now under siege by the United States and NATO. Madsen edits The Wayne Madsen Report and Tarpley is the author of Obama: The Postmodern Coup - Making of a Manchurian Candidate and other titles.

Today's broadcast went five minutes into a 4th hour overDrive.
